WARNING!

Since the policy about i18n on archlinux wiki has changed, this script
is irrelevant. However, I keep it online as an example and maybe for further developments.



Archdocumentalist generates wiki snapshots for a specific language.
The snapshot is a collection of html pages which are indexed in index.html.

USAGE:
archdocumentalist LANGUAGE PATH

where 
	LANGUAGE is a valid language code (EN, FR, DE...)
	See http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1
	PATH: output path

DEPENDANCES:
perl
perl-json-xs
perl-libwww

